{"tid":494771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[藝人眼中的明星] 雙宋 樸素美 權志龍 鄭河娜同聚IU演唱會","createTime":"2017-12-10T04:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T04:06:42.000Z","uid":34643,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48f2fd7bf9c567a553ed2387b350b0e6e6eb74af","tid":494771,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"或許好多網友仍然沉浸於宋仲基宋慧喬那場高顏值的婚禮，舉辦了婚禮之後的「雙宋夫婦」去了歐洲度蜜月，有網友偶遇他們，不過他們拍到的照片，有的照片宋慧喬戴著口罩，有的則是宋慧喬的背影，然而我們仍然能從這些照片里看出兩人的恩愛，比如天太冷，宋慧喬全程依偎著宋仲基取暖，時刻洋溢著幸福，而此次IU演唱會網友拍到的兩人照片，這可謂是兩人婚後首次露臉同框。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.xcnnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/20171210_5a2c9c9786c25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xcnnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F20171210_5a2c9c9786c25.jpg&h=cdec3f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩人的穿著打扮依舊低調，尤其是宋慧喬的穿著尤其注重保暖，但是儘管是路人拍的照片，而且宋慧喬看著是全素顏，但這絲毫不影響兩人的高顏值，再看宋仲基，他並沒有像有的網友所說的婚後有點發胖，身材看上去和我們熟悉的他差不多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.xcnnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/20171210_5a2c9c98341b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xcnnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F20171210_5a2c9c98341b5.jpg&h=0cd1e0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據現場的朋友說，「雙宋夫婦」坐在VIP座位上，宋仲基和IU早在2011年的時候就一起合作拍過廣告，宋仲基曾接受採訪表達過喜歡IU的音樂，宋慧喬的朋友在社交媒體上說IU的演唱會門票很難買，宋慧喬也留言說很想去看IU的演唱會，看來「雙宋夫婦」都是IU的粉絲，有這麼兩位大咖粉絲，想必IU將來的演唱會門票也會被迅速一搶而空。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.xcnnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/20171210_5a2c9c990d5fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xcnnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F20171210_5a2c9c990d5fe.jpg&h=df46341e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場的網友還曝了演唱會時兩人有趣的場景，他們起身要走的時候，前面的人和他們說還沒結束呢，他倆驚訝得睜大了眼睛，然後坐下來繼續看了，有的網友也著重觀察了宋慧喬的表情，看演唱會的時候她笑得很開心，宋仲基今年就說過，自己與宋慧喬有很多相似的地方，連喜歡IU的歌曲的興趣也都一樣。這會給無數的情侶們啟示，你們的性格是否相合，先看看彼此愛聽的歌曲是否相似"},{"pid":"8efbd89b543ef14a050641ec587c2ec702fe4630","tid":494771,"uid":34643,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:45:33.000Z","msg":"鄭河娜<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQmxLz4UQAEHjs8.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQmxLz4UQAEHjs8.jpg%3Aorig&h=f314f642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGD瞬間變怕醜仔 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tAq2E1Rmgpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtAq2E1Rmgpg&d=uDp64KopOkAOKSOp2j%2FPMXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=69b54e94\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tAq2E1Rmgpg</a><br />\n<br />\n朴率美<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fmb0kebsmaj30sc0scjsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fmb0kebsmaj30sc0scjsn.jpg&h=e9097fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n那樣小小的身體里怎麼會有那麼巨大的能量呢<br />\n那些深沉的想法到底是從幾歲開始有的呢<br />\n雖然不能具體的說出是哪些點<br />\n但是常常會覺得羡慕，感到安慰，又會覺得有些刺激到我<br />\n我還年輕（？）的時候要是有這種朋友就好了~我會邊思考我的人生，或許還會有某種成長也說不定~<br />\n不管怎麼說！<br />\n今天真的特別帥氣<br />\n我的眼睛和耳朵都非常享受<br />\n以後也會一直一直為你應援的<br />\n明天最後一場演唱會也要加油！<br />\n這麼說顯得有點陌生啊&hellip;kk<br />\n本來想直接走的，不過後來還是鼓起勇氣去後台照了認證照然後紅著臉跑出來了<br />\nIU演唱會#小知恩 再見啦"},{"pid":"41edaf038ad8bcb0254634c3e34f4568a4c5ba87","tid":494771,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"IU墊腳讓保鏢大叔傳話叫大家吃飯, 然後揮手再見最後像小孩子一樣被保鏢推走了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/6b103213gy1fmblf6uixyg205k096x6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F6b103213gy1fmblf6uixyg205k096x6g.jpg&h=5c26238f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/6b103213gy1fmblfcvj8fg20bq0ehkjn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F6b103213gy1fmblfcvj8fg20bq0ehkjn.jpg&h=11e6aa17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/6b103213gy1fmblfyvndbg206p0egb2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F6b103213gy1fmblfyvndbg206p0egb2c.jpg&h=a4aaca81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/6b103213gy1fmblgl22nfg20ba0e0x6s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F6b103213gy1fmblgl22nfg20ba0e0x6s.jpg&h=a048c88c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"251f849457bcec73de3013f785d0d25160ab67ae","tid":494771,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"171209 演員樸素美更新IU相關1P<br />\n紙花瓣掉下來了，悄悄打開了包包，包包里積了一層（kkkkkkk）。地獄般的周末，意外獲得手工材料。#謝謝#IU<br />\n翻譯:梨子<br />\nIU點贊 ​<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fmblfb8r1ij30hs0p5wgx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fmblfb8r1ij30hs0p5wgx.jpg&h=77d28a18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0da8a2de03b35247382b1ccce0b70cb74616e53","tid":494771,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:36:47.000Z","msg":"朴寶劍和李鍾碩也來IU演唱會了<br />\n炮哥在演唱會現場看到的<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/61ad358bgy1fmbrln06bhj20jv0adta1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F61ad358bgy1fmbrln06bhj20jv0adta1.jpg&h=94556c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEXID朴正花也來IU演唱會了<br />\n這位也是多次表白IU的迷妹了 <br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/61ad358bgy1fmbs3xd73bj20sg0sg11i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F61ad358bgy1fmbs3xd73bj20sg0sg11i.jpg&h=3624f1a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f122182ac7dad8653c4a0738a1e9d43a2d6cade2","tid":494771,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://instagram.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/t51.2885-15/e35/25007508_1986592761365781_3618195675533017088_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F25007508_1986592761365781_3618195675533017088_n.jpg&h=b7da5d50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid